State of North Carolina
v.
Soyer Lewis Moll No. 107P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 9, 2016 Jess D. Mekeel, Assistant Attorney General, Ernie Lee, District Attorney, For State of North Carolina. Soyer Lewis Moll, For Moll, Soyer Lewis.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 23rd of March 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Onslow County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of June 2016."

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 23rd of March 2016 by Defendant-Appellant to Appoint Counsel:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of June 2016."
